    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Your charming self and cheering love drew me to run to You"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "I thought I could be absolute"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "But how I’ve failed, how I’ve stumbled"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "To run this race divine by self"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Now I abhor myself"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "“Look away unto Me” (Hebrew 12:2)"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "I just cannot prevail"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "“It is by My Spirit” (Zechariah 4:6)"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "I am faithless, You’re faithful still (2 Tim 2:13)"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Your love is stronger than my will."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "We consecrate anew"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Do train, conform us to You"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "“May we be like the morning dew,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "“How I love You”"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Young people satisfying You.” (Psalm 110:3)"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Your gracious gifts, Your holy calls are irrevocable (Roman 11:29)"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Though I am not but You are able"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "From strength to strength, grace upon grace (Psalm 84:7, John 1:16)"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Sustaining me to win the race"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "My life I give to You"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "“I will never leave you” (Hebrew 13:5)"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "My dreams and future, too"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "“Nor will I forsake you” (Hebrew 13:5)"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Oh Lord I do! I do! I do!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "I love You Lord I really do."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
